oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Grand Ole Opry at the Alabama State Fair commercials
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Four commercials advertising appearances by Grand Ole Opry performers at the Alabama State Fair, read by Grant Turner. Performers said to appear include Pee Wee King and his Golden West Cowboys, Cowboy Copas, Grandpa Jones, Lew Childre, Stringbean, the Duke Of Paducah, and George D. Hay.
